# Open Source Dashboard — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A local web dashboard that helps you discover, learn, and contribute to open source projects in **AI / LLMs / Automation**.

![Dashboard Screenshot](/Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0ba4e217-c988-41df-93c1-62def8e3699c/dashboard_top_view_1770847293683.png)

![Dashboard Demo](/Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/brain/0ba4e217-c988-41df-93c1-62def8e3699c/dashboard_preview_1770847176837.webp)

## Dashboard Sections

| Section | What It Shows |
|---------|--------------|
| 📊 **Profile** | Your GitHub stats — repos, followers, join date |
| 📦 **Your Repos** | All 7 of your public repositories |
| 🔥 **Trending AI Repos** | Hot repos in AI/LLM space (AutoGen, n8n, LangChain, etc.) |
| 🏷️ **Good First Issues** | Beginner-friendly issues from 6 major projects |
| 🗺️ **Learning Roadmap** | Step-by-step path from beginner → advanced |

### Issue Sources
Good first issues are pulled from: **LangChain**, **Ollama**, **n8n**, **Hugging Face**, **Open WebUI**, **AutoGPT**

## How to Use

### Run the dashboard
```bash
cd /Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard
./run.sh
```
Then open **http://localhost:8787** in your browser.

### Refresh data only
```bash
./fetch-data.sh
```

## Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [index.html](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard/index.html) | Dashboard page |
| [style.css](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard/style.css) | Dark theme styling |
| [app.js](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard/app.js) | Loads data and renders the UI |
| [fetch-data.sh](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard/fetch-data.sh) | Fetches live data from GitHub |
| [run.sh](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/opensource-dashboard/run.sh) | One-command launcher |

